Order price = limit order of (trigger price + specified spread)
Set a tracking amount, stop loss price dynamically tracks market price changes.
· When market price falls, stop loss price also falls;
· When market price rises, stop loss price remains unchanged;
· When market price continues to rise to or above stop loss price, system will automatically submit;

